section.para:
In configure IronBee in nginx you must edit the nginx.conf to bootstrap the IronBee
            library.### nginx.conf

...

http {
    # Bootstrap the IronBee library
    ironbee_config_file /usr/local/ironbee/etc/ironbee-httpd.conf;

    # Setup logging
    ironbee_logger On;
    ironbee_loglevel 4;

    ...
}
